<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="R" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Richmond" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Richmond,</orth> name of an English earldom: <bibl n="shak. jn 2.552" default="NO" valid="yes">John II, 552</bibl>. <emph>Henry Earl of R.,</emph> afterwards King Henry VII: <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.6.67" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 6, 67</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.6.67" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 6, 67</bibl> <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.6.67" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C IV, 6, 67</bibl> <bibl n="shak. r3 4.1.43" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 IV, 1, 43</bibl> etc. His mother, the Countess R., married to Lord Stanley: <bibl n="shak. r3 1.3.20" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 3, 20</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>